                    <name>richTextValue</name>
                    <value>Hi&amp;nbsp;{{{Recipient.FirstName}}},&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
You are due for follow-up blood work.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Please find your follow-up lab order form attached. With this, you can go to any convenient LabCorp location.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
To ensure accurate results, please fast for at least 8 &amp;ndash; 10 hours prior to your blood draw and please be hydrated.
&lt;ol&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Schedule blood draw 4-5 days post testosterone injection&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;If using HGH, inject it within a 2-5 hour window of blood draw&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Please take ALL 10X Health prescribed oral medications in AM prior to blood draw&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;If using any cremes, do not apply to arms the AM of blood draw&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
You can find your nearest LabCorp location by &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.labcorp.com/labs-and-appointments-advanced-search&quot;&gt;CLICKING HERE&lt;/a&gt;.&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Make sure you print out and take the attached LabCorp lab order form with you.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
No appointment is required. Walk-ins are accepted.&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Please contact us if you have any questions or concerns.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
To your wellness,&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;10&lt;span style=&quot;color:#c0392b;&quot;&gt;X&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;Health System&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br aria-hidden=&quot;true&quot; /&gt;
